Pinterest is a place of endless possibilities. You can:
- Discover everyday inspiration
- Shop styles you love
- Try and learn something new

Create boards, save Pins and make collages of all your inspiration. Unlock billions of ideas, from fashion tips and easy recipes to DIY projects and fresh ways to redo your space. Creating the life you love? 

It's Possible.

MATCH, CHAT & DATE. IT STARTS WITH A SWIPE™.
With 97+ billion matches to date, Tinder® is the top free dating app and the best place to meet new people, with safety features that work to help you date more safely. Looking for love? An open relationship? Trying to find a date or new friends to chat with? Connect with local people everywhere on Tinder and get the best out of your dating experience:

Come As You Are: whether you're straight, gay, bisexual or anything in between, you can be who you are and find who you want on Tinder.
Date Beyond Photos: share your interests and learn more about your matches to get the conversation started.
Seek What You’re Looking For: set your relationship goals and make connections on your terms.

HOW TINDER WORKS
It’s easy and fun to find new people on Tinder®. Express yourself to make your personality shine in your profile and stand out to potential matches. Answer a prompt, share a little about you and show your face in your pics to increase your match-making potential. Use the Swipe Right™ feature to like and the Swipe Left™ feature to nope. If they like you back, It’s a Match! And with our double opt-in feature, it’s only a match if the interest is mutual.

PUT SAFETY FIRST
Try some of our safety features to help you make connections more confidently:

– Share My Date: share date plans with friends and fam, so they know who you’re planning to meet up with and where
– Get Photo Verified: verify your photos to help potential matches know it’s really you in that cute pic & increase your chances of matching
– Are You Sure / Does This Bother You: Tinder detects inappropriate language so people think twice before sending a disrespectful message
– Report a Profile: quickly report and block profiles with suspicious activity or inappropriate behaviour
– Block Contacts: take control and block anyone (like an ex) you don’t want to see on the app
– Video Chat: hitting it off in chat? Test your online dating chemistry and meet new people from home!

TRY TINDER PLUS
– Unlimited likes for you to catch feelings for as many new people as you want
– Use Passport Mode™ to match and chat with locals anywhere in the world before you arrive
– Unlimited Rewinds to undo your last like or nope
– Go Incognito and be seen only by the people you like

EXPERIENCE TINDER GOLD
– Get everything in Tinder Plus™, and try it out for a week before you commit to a monthly subscription
– See who likes you and match with them on the spot for faster connections
– Monthly Boost puts your profile to the top for 30 minutes to help increase your profile views
– Weekly Super Likes, because sometimes you really, really like someone

UPGRADE TO TINDER PLATINUM
Get most of Tinder’s premium features: join Tinder Platinum™ to get your likes prioritised with potential matches, send them a compliment before matching and more.

So what are you waiting for? Join millions of people worldwide! Tinder offers the most daters, increasing your chances of finding exactly what you're looking for. Download the best free dating app today!

––––––––––––––––––––
If you choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™ or Tinder Platinum™, payment will be charged to your Apple account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the App Store after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period. If you don’t choose to purchase Tinder Plus®, Tinder Gold™ or Tinder Platinum™, you can simply continue using Tinder for free.

All photos are of models and used for illustrative purposes only.

Quick Link is a comprehensive product that combines the functions of scanning and creating QR codes, aiming to provide users with a convenient and efficient QR code experience.

QR Code Scanning
Fast Recognition: Quick Link uses advanced image recognition technology to quickly and accurately scan and recognize the information in the QR code.
Multi-functional support: It supports scanning QR codes containing URL, text, phone number, SMS, email address and other information to meet the diversified needs of users.

QR Code Creation
Flexible editing: Users can customize the QR code with text, URL, contact information, etc. according to their needs.
One-click generation: After editing, users can simply click one-click generation to get their own QR code.

Efficient and Convenient
1. Quick Link's fast and accurate scanning and creation capability greatly improves users' efficiency in handling QR codes.
2. The simple and easy-to-use interface design makes it easy for users to get started without complicated operations.
Multi-functional Integration
1. Integrates scanning and creation functions to meet the needs of users in different scenarios.
2. supports the processing of QR codes of various information types to meet the diversified information interaction needs of users.
Secure and Reliable
1. adopts advanced encryption technology to ensure user information security.
2. Strict data protection mechanism ensures that user information will not be leaked or abused.

Kidslox parental control app is the perfect way to manage your family’s screen time. Our parental controls let you block apps, block internet access, and filter web content with ease.

Kidslox gives you control over your family’s device usage. Filter web content, block apps or websites, set weekly schedules with screen time limits, and see what your kids do with their devices, all from one place.

Kidslox new Screen Time Rewards feature encourages your kids to do their homework and household chores! 

As the first multi-platform parental controls, Kidslox gives you remote control over iPhones from other devices or vice-versa.

One account is all you need to manage your family’s screen time. Add up to 10 iPhones, iPads, iPods and other mobile devices and control your devices using the Kidslox app or any desktop or mobile web browser.

The Kidslox location tracker helps you keep your family safe offline as well as online. 

Prioritize your family time now by taking a moment to place daily limits on your child’s screen time. Parental control has never been so easy.

Kidslox features:

Screen Time Controls
• Set daily screen time limits
• Give screen time rewards for completed chores
• Use Schedules for device free homework time, dinnertime, bedtime and family time

Family Location Tracker
• See the location of your kids’ devices on the map
• Get notifications when your kids leave or arrive at preset zones

Parental Controls
• See what your child's been doing on their device
• Switch between different restriction levels at the touch of a button
• Stop your clever kids from changing the restrictions with a unique Kidslox PIN

Content Blocker
• Disable disruptive apps individually
• Filter pornography, gambling, violence and other adult content to give your child a safe browser experience
• Block internet access completely for added safety 
• Block in-app purchases
• Block Instagram, Facebook, Snapchat and other social networks
• Block games like Minecraft, Clash of Clans and Pokémon Go

Cross-Platform Coverage
• Keep your child or teen safe across devices
• Add up to 10 devices
• Manage all devices from one app or web browser

EXPERTS LOVE KIDSLOX

Recommended by ITV This Morning Parenting Expert Sue Atkins, Sarah Ockwell-Smith, Mother of four, Parenting Expert and bestselling author of six parenting books and Amber Mac, Canadian TV personality and technology commentator.

To use Kidslox you will need to download the app onto each device you wish to control. One paid account allows you to control up to 10 devices.

Kidslox contains no advertisements.

Kidslox parental control app offers a 3-day free trial of all Premium features. When the trial is over, access to features requires a subscription, with discounts for longer commitments.

Subscription and payment are made via your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase and subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Otherwise, the account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Cancellation of the current subscription is not allowed during the active subscription period. 'Lifetime subscription' does not auto-renew but gives ongoing access to Premium features for a one-off payment.

Help and Support:
Once you have downloaded Kidslox you will find all the help and online support you need from inside the app under our Help section.

Find copies of our terms and conditions using the link below: https://kidslox.com/terms/ and privacy policy here: https://kidslox.com/privacy-policy/

Kidslox requires an internet connection to operate

If a device has already been set up with an education or business MDM profile (Mobile Device Management) then you will not be able to add Kidslox unless you remove the original profile.

Spark connection, laughter, and intimacy with Loverzz, the all-in-one app for couples.

Whether you are in a long-distance relationship, newlyweds, or dating, Loverzz helps you grow closer through daily games, home screen widgets, and deep conversations.

Discover what your partner really thinks. One partner answers, the other guesses. Match answers to score points, unlock relationship insights, and ignite meaningful conversations.

DRAWING & WIDGETS
Send love notes directly to your partner's Home Screen. Use our drawing tools to sketch cute doodles or send photo widgets to keep your presence felt, no matter the distance. It is the perfect way to stay connected throughout the day without saying a word.

DAILY QUESTIONS & QUIZZES
From Future Dreams to Intimacy, explore over 13 categories designed to spark conversation. You answer honestly, your partner guesses your answer to see who knows who best. It turns serious relationship building into a fun, low-pressure game.

RELATIONSHIP INSIGHTS
Track your connection across 6 key dimensions: Vision, Intimacy, Adventure, Life Habits, Social Dynamics, and Crisis Management. Watch your understanding grow with visual progress tracking and compatibility scores.

PERFECT FOR LONG DISTANCE
Bridge the gap with digital interactions. The combination of real-time quizzes and Home Screen widgets makes Loverzz the ultimate tool for long-distance couples to stay synced and close, even when miles apart.

13 CONVERSATION CATEGORIES
Avoid running out of things to say. Our card packs range from fun to profound, including Future Dreams, Relationship Growth, Social Situations, Travel Adventures, Family, Career, and Intimacy.

WHY CHOOSE LOVERZZ
- Daily couples questions to build connection rituals
- Drawing and photo widgets for your Home Screen
- Deep conversation starters mixed with fun games
- Designed specifically for couples who want to grow closer

Join thousands of couples making Loverzz their daily habit. Because truly knowing your partner is the ultimate relationship goal.

Download Loverzz now and start your journey to a deeper connection.

Create your 3D plans easily and free of charge with the HomeByMe application. Ideal for designing the layout of an apartment or house, you can furnish your interior with real brands, create a 2D and 3D plan and then generate a 4K image of your project as if you were there!

HomeByMe is a fully featured 3D interior design tool. With a large community, partnerships with the most famous brands and a powerful design software, HomeByMe is the ultimate home design 3D application for deco lovers. Benefit from a brand catalog of over 30,000 products and a powerful 3D design engine.

From inspiration to creation, we're with you every step of the way. Find decorating ideas thanks to our community of over 5 million users, then share your creations with others!

Download our 3D modeling house application to find your house designs projects wherever you are and never miss the latest trends.

IMAGINE YOUR FUTURE INTERIOR BY CREATING YOUR PROJECT DIRECTLY ON YOUR MOBILE.

Design the interior of your dreams, from a studio to a castle, furnish it with design and trendy furniture from our catalog of more than 20,000 products: Maison du Monde, Wayfair, Katy Kuo Home, La Redoute Intérieur, Westwing... Find the new decorating trends and design news in our catalog and create the project that suits you. Hollywood Regency, Mid-Century Modern, Contemporary, Minimalist, Boho... explore a multitude of styles, share your creations with our community and inspire others.

Discover our unique features:
* Create realistic HD and 4K images 
* Generate HD and 4K aerial views in 2D and 3D
* Take a virtual tour of your home with 3D videos 
* Scan your room using Lidar technology (only available on IPhone 12 pro and above) and obtain your 3D floor plan directly
* Use artificial intelligence to get personalized furnishing suggestions
* Access to the 3D design inspiration feed
* Access to the 3D design furniture catalog
* Creation of 3D plan
* 3D design home: furnish and decorate the interior created
* Furnish automatically your room with the Magic Furnish feature
* Create your own collections and share them
* Sharing of realistic images

Share your creations on social networks, show your talents as a decorator and inspire others. You may then be selected for our Ambassador program and gain a larger audience

WOULD YOU LIKE TO SAVE TIME ON YOUR INTERIOR DESIGN OR RENOVATION PROJECT? 

HomeByMe lets you create your new interior quickly, by suggesting layouts based on your tastes and preferences. Thanks to the AutoDesign feature, you can now furnish a room using images from the community to pick up decorating ideas. Select the images you like and then choose the proposal that suits you best. You can then modify it as you wish and adapt it to your interior. 

For a wow effect, use our video virtual tour feature. Once you've created your 3D design, you can generate a video (also in 3D) to show you around your home. Send it out and share it with others to gather opinions and advice. It's the ideal feature for a renovation: project yourself straight into your new interior as if you were there!

LOOKING FOR A MORE PROFESSIONAL USE?

The HomeByMe app allows you to store your clients' projects and access them 24 hours a day, wherever you are. Edit them live, with them, and show them the result. The mobile-friendly planner allows you to quickly and easily make corrections according to your clients' desires. Involve them in the design of their project, create realistic images and let them project themselves, as if they were there.

Want to save time? Visit your customers' homes, scan their rooms and obtain a 3D plan directly to scale, without having to go through the design stage: all you have to do is decorate according to your customers' requirements.

The Microsoft Family Safety app helps empower you and your family to create healthy habits and protect the ones you love. Get peace of mind that your family is staying a little safer while giving your kids independence.
